Class Camp

java.lang.Object
Camp
public class Camp extends Object
Represents a Camp within the Camp Application System. A Camp is created by a Staff.
Since:
20/11/23

      The Staff member who created this Camp.

    • visible

      private boolean visible
      The visibility setting of this Camp. true indicates eligible Students are able to see this Camp in their available camps. false indicates all Students are not able to see this Camp in their available camps. Staff that created this Camp is able to view this Camp regardless of its visbility status.

    • setVisibility

      public void setVisibility(boolean visibility)
      Changes the visibility of this Camp. true indicates this Camp will appear in the list of available Camps for members of this Camp's User groups. false indicates this Camp will not appear in the list of available Camps for any Students. This Camp's Staff is able to view the Camp regardless of its visibility.
      Parameters:
      visibility - whether this Camp is visible to Students.
